column2: This image shows an ivory-colored sectional sofa with a matching armchair on a white rug. There are decorative pillows on the sofa, and a small glass bottle and a couple of glasses on the rug. The image includes a color code (86KP / Ivory") and a model number ("#1707") on the bottom. There are no visible phone numbers, URLs, or any content related to hate, violence, self-harm, or adult themes. Classification: Safe"
